{"type":null,"faqId":49388,"title":"管理主屏幕小工具和图标","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"增加小工具\"XE \"删除小工具\"XE \"删除图标\"XE \"创建文件夹\"XE \"桌面小工具\"XE \"窗口小部件\"XE \"窗口小工具\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>背景信息</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若要在主屏幕添加小工具或文件夹，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">添加小工具</span><span>：在主屏幕，两指捏合进入主屏幕编辑状态。点击“窗口小工具”，选择一个小工具，它将添加到主屏幕的空白区域。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188939\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>主屏幕中需有足够的空间来放置窗口小工具，如果空间不足，请先添加主屏幕或释放主屏幕空间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">移动小工具或图标</span><span>：在主屏幕，长按一个窗口小工具或图标直到手机振动，然后将其拖动到主屏幕任意位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">删除小工具或图标</span><span>：在主屏幕，长按要删除的窗口小工具或图标，直到屏幕上方出现“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188940\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，然后将其拖动到“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188941\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">创建文件夹</span><span>：在主屏幕，拖动一个图标到另一个图标上，两个图标将集合在一个新文件夹中。打开文件夹，长按文件夹名称可重命名文件夹。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">隐藏应用程序图标</span><span>：在主屏幕，两指分开进入隐藏应用程序图标界面，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188942\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，勾选要隐藏的应用程序，然后点击“确定”。应用程序图标隐藏后，将不显示在主屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1090,"faqType":"开始使用","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5132","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Getting-know-phone","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294336000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":32,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}